headline: Top Toy Brand LITTLEST PET SHOP Signs Global YouTube Sensation
summary: LITTLEST PET SHOP, the iconic collectible toy brand known for inspiring creativity and storytelling through its quirky bobblin' pets, today announced Like Nastya, one of the most popular child creators in the world, has signed on as an official brand partner.
